MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7e8140d05737a11468020c371c32ff33, type: 3}
  m_Name: Resolve_E1_DelCruz
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: AQ.App::AQ.App.CaseGraph
  startId: E1_L9_N1
  stageBackground: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b61e15d0a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0e108, type: 3}
  nodes:
  - id: E1_L9_N1
    speaker: "Ally Quinn"
    line: "Sergeant Del Cruz, Harbor Ward, her lunch break, her bench — back to the water. I laid it out: the forty seconds, the inspector, the van, the coin now in her evidence intake."
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 792b5f88f6dd2724d84b6954cc0b5fad, type: 3}
    emotion: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: 
    nextId: E1_L9_N2
    choices: []
  - id: E1_L9_N2
    speaker: "Del Cruz"
    line: "I can open the missing-person file — empty house, packed bag, that footage. That's real. What I can't do is turn your theory about boats into warrants. Not on a podcast's say-so."
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: de1a4b5c6d7e8f90a1b2c3d4e5f6a701, type: 3}
    emotion: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: 
    nextId: E1_L9_N3
    choices: []
  - id: E1_L9_N3
    speaker: "Ally Quinn"
    line: "Then the question that cuts this episode in half. He already knows I heard him — I told the whole city I have his footsteps. What he doesn't know is how cleanly. The full track holds his engine, his gait, the room itself. Publish it, and ten thousand ears go to work. So does he."
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: e02460f0c092dde4891723eecbbdc368, type: 3}
    emotion: 5
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: 
    nextId: E1_L9_N4
    choices: []
  - id: E1_L9_N4
    speaker: "Del Cruz"
    line: "Your show, your call. Just don't pretend silence is neutral either."
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: de1a4b5c6d7e8f90a1b2c3d4e5f6a701, type: 3}
    emotion: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: 
    nextId: 
    choices:
    - text: "Release the full recording — let the city work it"
      nextId: E1_L9_N5A
      requiresFlag: 
    - text: "Publish a transcript only — Del keeps the clean copy"
      nextId: E1_L9_N5B
      requiresFlag: 
  - id: E1_L9_N5A
    speaker: "Ally Quinn"
    line: "We released it at noon. By mid-afternoon, a retired Harbourline fleet mechanic had named the engine — the governor retrofit their vans carried after the '09 recall. Hours, not days. The cost came with it: two hundred false sightings, and the van off the streets by dusk."
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 792b5f88f6dd2724d84b6954cc0b5fad, type: 3}
    emotion: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: aq.e1.truth_public
    nextId: E1_L9_N6
    choices: []
  - id: E1_L9_N5B
    speaker: "Ally Quinn"
    line: "We published the transcript and held the audio. By evening Del had walked the clean copy and the plate through properly: the plate is registered to a shell contractor, but the VIN traces back to a van last registered to Harbourline. Slower than the crowd. Cleaner than the noise. And he still doesn't know what we hold."
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 792b5f88f6dd2724d84b6954cc0b5fad, type: 3}
    emotion: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: aq.e1.truth_protected
    nextId: E1_L9_N6
    choices: []
  - id: E1_L9_N6
    speaker: "Ally Quinn"
    line: "Either way, one thing rides with me now: how you tell the truth is also who you are. Dot's still out there — and her car never left the drive. So how does a frightened woman with a church case leave town?"
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 792b5f88f6dd2724d84b6954cc0b5fad, type: 3}
    emotion: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag: 
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag: aq.lead.e1_delcruz.seen
    nextId: 
    choices: []
